\section*{Summary}

\begin{frame}{Summary}
  \begin{itemize}
  \item
    A position on \alert{what it is for an intention to be an occurrent intention at a time and an account of the persistence of occurrent intentions to A as occurrent intentions to A}.
  \item
    A sufficient condition for \alert{something’s being a standing intention to A}.
  \item
    Discussion of \alert{Relatively short-term standing intentions}.
  \end{itemize}
  
  \begin{itemize}
  \item
    Outlook
    \begin{itemize}
    \item
      Explore long term counterparts of persisting standing intentions.
    \end{itemize}
  \end{itemize}
\end{frame}



